Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.37,0:24:16.95,Main03,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.95,0:24:19.38,Main03,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to bear\Nwatching you tied up,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.38,0:24:23.27,Main03,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,abused, stabbed, and\Nsuffering next week!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.27,0:24:25.13,Main03,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sit idly by anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.13,0:24:26.36,Main03,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,Please shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.36,0:24:27.26,Main03,Kami,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.26,0:24:28.04,Main03,Okita,0000,0000,0000,,The next episode...
